Key figures In fiscal 2023, which ended on September 30, 2023, Siemens

generated revenues of €78 billion and profits after tax of €8.5 billion. As of September 30, 2023, the company had approximately 320,000 employees worldwide. SIEMENS FINANCIAL REPORT FISCAL 2023, COMBINED MANAGEMENT REPORT, CHAPTER 7, OVERALL ASSESSMENT OF THE ECONOMIC POSITION

Customers Putting customers first is a longstanding tradition at

Siemens.1 When it comes to technology, sustainability, and innovation, our customers are always at the heart of what we think and do: everything begins with them. That is why we have made “customer impact” a strategic priority. We listen to understand our customers’ needs as early as possible, and ideally, before our customers even become aware of them.